ase keep in mind that this project isn't complete. I just need to work in some of my weak points, then, you'll be the first looking at the final product.<br>
<br>
Also, this story is inspired in many games and manga titles such as: Final Fantasy, Metal Gear Solid and Rurouni Kenshin, but all the background itself isn't exactly a mix... it looks kind of original. Here we go...<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>  THE MAN... THE MYTH... THE LEGEND:</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
This is the story of Chad Wright, a man once declared the greatest sniper and soldier of all time. After a severe amnesia prior to his career in the army, Chad starts to put the pieces of his memory together to find out his real identity. The man's real purpose was to forge a future free of wars and betrayals... but then the major commanders of his unit decided to brainwash him to create the perfect assassin.<br>
<br>
5 years after he escaped the living terror of war, Chad moved to a small town in California, looking for some peace. There's only one thing that reminds him of his past...  the voice of his war buddy, Michael Harrison, also known as &quot;Leviathan&quot; the infiltration expert.<br>
<br>
Unfortunately, Michael was brainwashed too, and his friendship with Chad became just a weird and familiar nightmare. Only destiny can cross the path of these men once again, a fight to stop another fights... a fight to put an end to THE END OF THE WORLD.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>  IT CAN'T BE!!!:</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
After the end of the Anti-Terrorist war, the UN created SHOCK to stop any other treat similar to the ones in the past. The General, Roger Hunter, decided to call &quot;Sniper Hawk&quot; and &quot;Leviathan&quot; out of their retirement to get back on duty once again. The whole process is called &quot;Project Revival&quot;, a program paid by the US and Russian Governments for military purposes.<br>
<br>
The mission: Infiltrate an old weapons factory and take any possible information out of a man known as &quot;Dr. Gorou&quot;, a rebel scientist working in another project called &quot;Maxima Eagle&quot;. Then, SHOCK must kill him and retrieve the corpse immediately.<br>
<br>
But this mission is just a cover.... the real purposes of this operation are hidden, even to the US President. What is it? What's the real objective of Project Revival?<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>  The Characters:</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
Sniper Hawk: The man once known as Chad Wright. One of the greatest soldiers of all time, killing against his own will. Hawk has succeeded in many operations, but Project Revival might be another story.<br>
<br>
Leviathan: The warm-hearted Michael Harrison is just a cover to the moving shadow that lives inside him. He can successfully infiltrate harsh environments, no matter what's the cost.<br>
<br>
Stealth Dragon: A master of the mystical arts of the Ninja brought from Feudal Japan to the present thanks to the genetic technology of SHOCK. Little is known about this mysterious man.<br>
<br>
Revolver Maximus: A cowboy with a formidable gunfiring ability. Back in his era, he earned respect thanks to several massacres and victories in bar brawls. However, this man got betrayed by his friend and died in an ambush.<br>
<br>
Assault Spider: An expert in massive assaul tactics and raids. There isn't an precise description of the man, except that he's always smiling, while staring at the corpses of his opponents. The only member of the Project that actually accepted the mission voluntarily. <br>
<br>
Remember this isn't complete, and sorry if the whole storyline isn't clear (Remember I'm doing my best). I guess that's all, see ya later.<br>
